{"sha": "914966e499dfe0861127447bc72c9071e80a4a9b", "node_id": "MDY6Q29tbWl0MTM2NTMxMDA6OTE0OTY2ZTQ5OWRmZTA4NjExMjc0NDdiYzcyYzkwNzFlODBhNGE5Yg==", "commit": {"author": {"name": "Patrick Palka", "email": "ppalka@redhat.com", "date": "2020-07-23T14:38:58Z"}, "committer": {"name": "Patrick Palka", "email": "ppalka@redhat.com", "date": "2020-07-23T17:34:00Z"}, "message": "contrib/vimrc: detect more C-like files\n\nCurrently this script doesn't set the indentation style for the standard\nlibrary headers under libstdc++/ because they lack a file extension.\nBut they do have a modeline, so the file type is still set appropriately\nby Vim.  So by inspecting &filetype, we can also detect these standard\nlibrary headers as C-like files.\n\ncontrib/ChangeLog:\n\n\t* vimrc (SetStyle): Also inspect &filetype to determine whether\n\ta file is C-like.", "tree": {"sha": "80a4b8941aef4f7a91946cfa865eda101854e28c", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/trees/80a4b8941aef4f7a91946cfa865eda101854e28c"}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/git/commits/914966e499dfe0861127447bc72c9071e80a4a9b", "comment_count": 0, "verification": {"verified": false, "reason": "unsigned", "signature": null, "payload": null}}, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/914966e499dfe0861127447bc72c9071e80a4a9b", "html_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commit/914966e499dfe0861127447bc72c9071e80a4a9b", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/914966e499dfe0861127447bc72c9071e80a4a9b/comments", "author": null, "committer": null, "parents": [{"sha": "084dc63a0200e60e0fbb7c36b412a158d234f5c0", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commits/084dc63a0200e60e0fbb7c36b412a158d234f5c0", "html_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/commit/084dc63a0200e60e0fbb7c36b412a158d234f5c0"}], "stats": {"total": 2, "additions": 1, "deletions": 1}, "files": [{"sha": "356d455b059cd5737eebeda8a7ab0e0a119898bf", "filename": "contrib/vimrc", "status": "modified", "additions": 1, "deletions": 1, "changes": 2, "blob_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/blob/914966e499dfe0861127447bc72c9071e80a4a9b/contrib%2Fvimrc", "raw_url": "https://github.com/Rust-GCC/gccrs/raw/914966e499dfe0861127447bc72c9071e80a4a9b/contrib%2Fvimrc", "contents_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/Rust-GCC/gccrs/contents/contrib%2Fvimrc?ref=914966e499dfe0861127447bc72c9071e80a4a9b", "patch": "@@ -45,7 +45,7 @@ function! SetStyle()\n     setlocal textwidth=80\n   endif\n   setlocal formatoptions-=ro formatoptions+=cqlt\n-  if index(l:c_exts, l:ext) != -1\n+  if index(l:c_exts, l:ext) != -1 || &filetype == \"c\" || &filetype == \"cpp\"\n     setlocal cindent\n     setlocal cinoptions=>4,n-2,{2,^-2,:2,=2,g0,f0,h2,p4,t0,+2,(0,u0,w1,m0\n   endif"}]}